SEARCH
Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Class JSPCodeGenerator

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp.JSPCodeGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
JSPElementVisitor
public class JSPCodeGenerator extends Object implements JSPElementVisitor
Generates Java servlet source code from a JSP Abstract Syntax Tree.

This class takes a JSPPage object (the parsed JSP AST) and generates the corresponding Java servlet source code that implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet. The generated servlet can then be compiled and loaded to handle JSP requests.

The code generator handles various JSP elements:

  • TextElement - Static HTML/text content → out.write() calls
  • ScriptletElement - Java code blocks → Direct insertion into service method
  • ExpressionElement - Java expressions → out.write(String.valueOf()) calls
  • DeclarationElement - Java declarations → Class-level fields and methods
  • DirectiveElement - Page directives → Imports, content type, session handling
  • CommentElement - JSP comments → Java comments or ignored
  • StandardActionElement - JSP standard actions → Method calls
Author:
Chris Burdess
